/" rel="tag">Zhang Guoyong</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="AKuan, Guo Wenjing, Han Peng, Il ragazzo del risci, Opera lirica, Song Yuangming, Sun Xiuwei, Tan Haojiang, teatro carlo felice di genova, Wang Qi, Yi Liming, Zhang Guoyong"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/a44c5de07732564a59a988ff766b2ff9" alt="" /> <img src="http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/a44c5de07732564a59a988ff766b2ff9?s=100&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="100" height="100" alt="" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 photo avatar-default" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Luca Baracchini"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/luca-baracchini/">View all articles by Luca Baracchini</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/10/liegi-opera-royale-de-wallonie-ernani/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Liegi, Opra Royale de Wallonie: &#8220;Ernani&#8221;</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/10/verona-il-settembre-dellaccademia-2015-i-virtuosi-italiani/" rel="next">Verona, Il Settembre dell&#8217;Accademia 2015: &#8220;I Virtuosi Italiani&#8221; <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div 